{
  "chapter": 54,
  "chapter_summary": "第五十四回\"试剑\"\n\n本章围绕小方与齐小燕两人各自练成独孤痴剑法后的命运交汇展开。开篇大年向小燕报告小方的异常状态——频繁洗冷水澡、脾气暴躁、精神萎靡——小燕对此心知肚明，面露神秘笑容。大年透露小方急切要见小燕，小燕当即决定前往。\n\n小燕来到荒山山巅的秘密清泉沐浴更衣，取出藏匿已久的崭新丝绸衣物。午后小方在枫林练剑，一剑刺穿树干。小燕出现祝贺他的剑法已成，两人确认交易结束。但小燕提出必须先去找独孤痴清算旧账，约定两人中活下来的人去执行。两人拔剑决斗。\n\n小燕试图以心理战术摧毁小方的信心——指出他因男性体质无法宣泄独孤痴剑法带来的精气郁结，必败无疑。小方反击指出小燕作为女性根本无法领悟独孤痴剑法的精髓，即便击败他也必将死在独孤痴剑下。心理战未能动摇对方。\n\n决斗正式开始，一百五十招后小方凭经验和耐力获胜。小燕败北瞬间真正体会到死亡的恐惧，情欲与恐惧交织产生奇异变化。战后两人在中秋月圆之夜有了肌肤之亲。天明鸡啼时小燕再次如幽灵般逃走，小方追出。章末转写独孤痴的苦修生活——石板床、简单食物、时刻保持清醒，以及他与\"小虫\"的复杂关系。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_nian",
      "speaker_name": "大年",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "是的。这个人最近好像忽然变得特别喜欢干净，每天都要洗好几次冷水澡。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_da_nian",
      "text": "男人洗冷水澡不一定是为了爱干净。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_nian",
      "speaker_name": "大年",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "不是为了爱干净是为了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_da_nian",
      "text": "你还是个小孩子，你不会懂的。大人的事，你最好也不要多问。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_da_nian",
      "text": "你看他最近有没有什么跟以前不一样的地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_nian",
      "speaker_name": "大年",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "好像有一点。最近他脾气好像变得特别暴躁，精神却好像比以前差了，眼睛总是红红的，就好像晚上从来都不睡觉一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_da_nian",
      "text": "今天他有没有问起我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_nian",
      "speaker_name": "大年",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "最近这一个月，他只要一见到我，第一句话就会问我见到你没有？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_nian",
      "speaker_name": "大年",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "今天他还说一定要你去见他，因为他有非常非常重要的事要见你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_nian",
      "speaker_name": "大年",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "看他的样子，就好像如果看不见你就马上会死掉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_da_nian",
      "text": "我知道。我当然知道。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_nian",
      "speaker_name": "大年",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "如果你不去，他是不是真的会死掉？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_da_nian",
      "text": "就算不死，一定也很难过。我想他最近的日子一定很难过。一天比一天难过，难过得要命。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_nian",
      "speaker_name": "大年",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "你要不要去见他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_da_nian",
      "text": "我要去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_nian",
      "speaker_name": "大年",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "什么时候去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_da_nian",
      "text": "今天就去。现在就去！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_da_nian",
      "text": "你的腿为什么在发抖？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_nian",
      "speaker_name": "大年",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "我害怕。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_da_nian",
      "text": "你怕什么？怕我？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_da_nian",
      "text": "你几时变得这么怕我的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_nian",
      "speaker_name": "大年",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "刚才。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_da_nian",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_nian",
      "speaker_name": "大年",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "因为……因为你刚才看起来就像要杀人的样子。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_da_nian",
      "text": "现在我看起来难道就不像要杀人的样子了？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "恭喜你。你的剑法已经练成了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "你呢？你的剑法是不是也练成了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是的。我的剑法也可以算是练成了，因为你已经没有什么可以教给我。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "我明白你的意思。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你明白？你说我是什么意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "现在我已经没有什么可以教给你，你也没有什么可以教给我，所以我们的交易已结束。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "我找你来，就为了要告诉你，我已经准备走了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你不能走。至少现在还不能走。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为我们还要去找独孤痴。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "所以我们两个人之间最少要有一个人去找他。也只能一个人去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为我是我，你是你，我们要找他的原因本来就不一样。我们之间本来就没有关系。我的事当然要我自己去解决，你不能代替我，我也不能代替你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "是你去！还是我去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "谁活着，谁就去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "现在我们两个人好像还全都活着。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "可惜我们之间必定有个人活不长的。我看得出片刻后我们之间就有个人会死在这里。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "死的是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "谁败了，谁就要死。你有剑，我也有。你已经练成了我的剑法，我也练成了你的剑法。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "现在是不是已经到了我们要比一比究竟是谁强谁弱的时候。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "谁败了，谁就死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是的。强者生，弱者生。这样是不是也很公平？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "是的，这样子的确公平极了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你有没有什么后事要交待给我？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我没有。因为我不会死的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "你有把握？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我当然有。否则我怎么会来？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你自己知不知道你为什么必败无疑？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为你是男人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "就因为我是男人，所以我就必败？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是的。就是这样子的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为你已经练过独孤痴的剑法。我说过，他的剑法很绝，也很邪。每隔一段日子，一定要将精气宣泄，身心才能保持平衡稳定。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "可是你的精气根本就没有发泄的地方。所以你最近已经渐渐变了，变得焦躁不安，就算一天冲十次冷水也没有用。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "一个人如果连自己的情绪都无法保持镇定，他能不能算是个可怕的对手？他怎么能不败！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "所以我才问你，你还有什么后事要交代？还有没有什么话要说？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "只有一句话。就算你能击败我，也必将死在独孤痴的剑下。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "因为你是女人！就因为你是女人，所以你永远没有击败他的机会。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "text": "因为他的剑法确实很绝，也很邪。我经过五个月后，就觉得有一股精气郁结。可是你没有。因为你是女人，根本就无法得到他剑法中的精髓。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小燕",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "不管怎么样，我好歹都要去试一试。所以现在我就要先用你来试一试我的剑！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 403
    }
